36 this chapter concerning coal combustion residuals. The rules adopted
37 under this subsection:
38 (1) shall be consistent with the regulations of the United States
39 Environmental Protection Agency concerning standards for the
40 disposal of coal combustion residuals in landfills and surface
41 impoundments, as set forth in the federal CCR rule;
42 (2) shall not impose a restriction or requirement that is more
